<p>Still need to add krb5 support. Let's wait until we know what we're
doing with kerberos installation.</p>

<p>On Darwin the configure option
<code>--with-password-timeout=0</code> is required to disable the
password timeout code, or else the password prompt hangs. The docs
claim that this is a bug in Darwin, so we should figure out what's
going on here.</p>
